{"tid":2060437,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瞞參與華千人計劃 哈佛教授遭美起訴","createTime":"2020-06-11T15:36:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T18:15:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"57f2502fa9ad7d8fd88808721f890e9758da343e","tid":2060437,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:36:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200611/JWHOVE3OWMZGE75YB3ZS2ULRI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200611%2FJWHOVE3OWMZGE75YB3ZS2ULRI4%2F&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0rrngSbsgLaTM31cPJ1174U%3D&h=8163d37e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200611%2FJWHOVE3OWMZGE75YB3ZS2ULRI4%2F&h=07ca15dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200611/JWHOVE3OWMZGE75YB3ZS2ULRI4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n瞞參與華千人計劃 哈佛教授遭美起訴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7HB5JQLIAPGCP2N7XXYBFDWIQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7HB5JQLIAPGCP2N7XXYBFDWIQM.jpg&h=c421c6e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利伯<br />\n<br />\n哈佛大學前化學系主任、世界頂級化學專家利伯（Charles Lieber）教授，涉嫌隱瞞自己參與中共「千人計劃」案，美國司法部前日正式控以虛假文書罪，案件將在波士頓聯邦法院提審。如罪名成立，他將面臨兩個最高五年的刑期、三年假釋及25萬美元（下同，約194萬港元）的罰款。其代表律師指當局做法錯誤，利伯是受害者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被控虛假文書罪<br />\n<br />\n起訴書指，今年1月被捕的利。。。。。。。。。。與中國的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n「千人計劃」是中共2008年推出、旨在募集海外高。。。。。。。。。。。自己在中共軍隊任職，偽造學生身份來美國做研究。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音"},{"pid":"d0e83b6ff62705244abf84f495ea08c13f826494","tid":2060437,"uid":53695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:50:49.000Z","msg":"侵仔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMore<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/p